    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those seeking a functional daily driver. While the exterior shows some signs of age with minor scratches and the interior has seen regular use, the engine starts up consistently and the transmission shifts through gears as expected. All major safety components are functional, though some non-essential features may require attention. It\u2019s a dependable car that provides honest transportation without the high price tag of a newer model.",
